# Documentation (Development Guides)
# ===========================
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md
# Ignore entire docs/ directory (development guides, not test docs)
docs/
/docs/

# ===========================
# Uppercase .md files (except README.md)
# ===========================
# Ignore all .md files that start with 3+ uppercase letters (e.g., TEST_STATUS.md, DATA_CONTRACT.md)
# But keep README.md files (they start with only 2 uppercase letters)
# Pattern matches files starting with 3+ uppercase letters: TEST_*.md, DATA_*.md, etc.
**/[A-Z][A-Z][A-Z]*.md
# Explicitly keep README.md files
!**/README.md
# Explicitly keep tests/docs/ directory (but only lowercase .md files)
!tests/docs/
!tests/docs/*.md
# Re-ignore uppercase files in tests/docs/ (override the above)
# Pattern: matches files starting with 3+ uppercase letters (e.g., STATUS_DEC20.md, TEST_STATUS.md)
tests/docs/[A-Z][A-Z][A-Z]*.md
# Explicitly allow status_dec20.md (lowercase, should be committed)
!tests/docs/status_dec20.md
